==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Proper noun===
'''Persia'''

#The [[country]] of [[Iran]] until 1935 was officially called "[[Persia]]" in Western languages. The native name of the country since Sassanian period is "[[Iran]]". Since 1935 both terms "Iran" and "Persia" have been used in English, though [[Iran]] predominates. The [[w:Persia|Persian Empire]] once included most of Western and [[Central Asia]] and [[North Africa]].

